(you're using and what its access speeds are like. A lot of my exposure to this dates from the) Tj
T*
(days of slow HDDs.\) This potential vast difference is why you want more detailed information in) Tj
T*
(both cache metrics and IO traces. The more narrowly you can attribute IO and the more you know) Tj
